      "writtenOn": "2026-03-18T18:50:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you eventually intended to merge this with the existing System class?  Or will they remain permanently separate.\n\nSeems like you have a system and at least one chassis regardless of the system type.",
      "revId": "6831d57687b99d886a2f7e6621289ba640b2da87",
