      "writtenOn": "2026-04-08T18:28:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Probably remain separate for now, just to avoid breaking any of the current single-chassis code. Plan is to hide the main loop for the multi-chassis code behind an ifdef that checks a meson compile flag and use either the main loop for single-chassis or multi-chassis code depending on the value of the flag.",
